						<summary>

						<p>On the <hi rend="italic">dhvajastambha</hi> in front of the Nārāyaṇadēva temple.</p>						

						<p>977 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 8[9]9, Īśvara, Jyēshṭha puṇṇami, Monday, Rōhiṇī-nakshatra corresponding to 977 A.D., June 4. The <hi rend="italic">nakscatra,</hi> however, was Mūlā.</p>						

						<p>It records the erection of a <hi rend="italic">mānastambha.</hi> The details are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
